WEBVTT

00:00:06.800 --> 00:00:07.400
So that means

00:00:07.400 --> 00:00:08.880
you never saw Qiao Sanbao's face

00:00:12.560 --> 00:00:14.119
He's usually very talkative

00:00:14.840 --> 00:00:16.959
but that night he didn't say a word

00:00:20.959 --> 00:00:22.639
When this handsome officer mentioned it,

00:00:23.200 --> 00:00:25.440
I thought back, and he did seem off that day

00:00:25.879 --> 00:00:26.319
Brother San

00:00:26.680 --> 00:00:28.440
Today's goods are pretty big

00:00:30.040 --> 00:00:31.120
He wasn't like Qiao Sanbao

00:00:31.120 --> 00:00:32.279
Watch what you say

00:00:34.360 --> 00:00:35.639
Um, officer

00:00:35.759 --> 00:00:37.919
Does this count as cooperating for leniency?

00:00:38.119 --> 00:00:39.400
Does that mean I can go now?

00:00:39.479 --> 00:00:40.439
What do you think?

00:00:47.680 --> 00:00:48.520
So now

00:00:48.520 --> 00:00:49.799
apart from that finger,

00:00:50.200 --> 00:00:53.400
we really found no more of Liu Ping's dismembered remains

00:00:54.400 --> 00:00:55.439
Could it be

00:00:56.639 --> 00:00:58.159
it really was the two siblings?

00:00:58.919 --> 00:00:59.720
But why?

00:01:02.720 --> 00:01:03.680
Any thoughts?

00:01:06.879 --> 00:01:09.639
Why would that finger be here?

00:01:12.599 --> 00:01:13.720
Could it have been just to

00:01:13.720 --> 00:01:15.639
throw off our investigation?

00:01:16.440 --> 00:01:17.559
Then this Liu Ping

00:01:18.120 --> 00:01:19.040
is really ruthless

00:01:20.879 --> 00:01:21.919
He looks unreliable,

00:01:22.160 --> 00:01:23.360
but he's got some brains

00:01:26.559 --> 00:01:27.400
Sorry about that

00:01:27.680 --> 00:01:28.800
I was just

00:01:29.040 --> 00:01:30.319
throwing out an idea

00:01:31.800 --> 00:01:32.279
Sister Lin

00:01:33.319 --> 00:01:34.639
do you think what I said makes sense?

00:01:38.480 --> 00:01:39.400
That's possible

00:01:40.879 --> 00:01:42.000
but we can't rule out an accident either

00:01:42.239 --> 00:01:43.559
Maybe we're overthinking it

00:01:44.120 --> 00:01:45.239
In the end, it all comes down to evidence

00:01:48.120 --> 00:01:48.639
Exactly

00:01:48.639 --> 00:01:49.800
Evidence is crucial

00:01:51.000 --> 00:01:51.639
Right now,

00:01:51.639 --> 00:01:52.360
no matter what,

00:01:52.360 --> 00:01:53.760
Liu Li is our breakthrough point

00:01:54.199 --> 00:01:56.199
Let's get her talking first

00:01:56.519 --> 00:01:57.040
Yes

00:02:01.279 --> 00:02:01.959
Lu Yi

00:02:04.919 --> 00:02:06.120
watch how you address me

00:02:10.160 --> 00:02:12.240
I don't want to hear "Sister Lin" again

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:15.880
Lin Meimei

00:02:21.880 --> 00:02:22.919
Comrade Lin

00:02:24.800 --> 00:02:25.600
Officer Lin

00:02:27.399 --> 00:02:28.320
beautiful Lin

00:02:33.119 --> 00:02:33.960
What were you doing?

00:02:33.960 --> 00:02:35.039
Why'd you take so long?

00:02:35.279 --> 00:02:36.440
Be serious in a minute

00:02:36.520 --> 00:02:37.479
Don't act so slick

00:02:37.880 --> 00:02:39.679
I went to get a prop

00:02:40.080 --> 00:02:41.160
Once we go in,

00:02:41.559 --> 00:02:42.559
I'll play good cop

00:02:42.919 --> 00:02:43.800
you play bad cop

00:02:45.800 --> 00:02:46.399
What's that?

00:02:47.039 --> 00:02:47.839
Secret for now

00:02:52.639 --> 00:02:54.080
Do you think those two

00:02:54.600 --> 00:02:55.320
can pull it off?

00:02:58.240 --> 00:03:00.080
It's happening right before you, and you ask me?

00:03:01.800 --> 00:03:02.320
Well, I...

00:03:03.240 --> 00:03:03.800
I just figured

00:03:03.800 --> 00:03:05.399
you forensic people have an eagle eye

00:03:05.520 --> 00:03:07.600
and see everything more clearly

00:03:13.759 --> 00:03:15.800
Don't drink milk tea like it's goji water every day

00:03:16.000 --> 00:03:16.880
Watch your blood sugar

00:03:21.520 --> 00:03:24.039
I can only see what's right in front of me

00:03:25.199 --> 00:03:25.960
Hello

00:03:27.679 --> 00:03:28.360
Come here right now

00:03:49.479 --> 00:03:50.119
Liu Li

00:03:50.639 --> 00:03:52.600
Where is your brother Liu Ping right now?

00:03:56.479 --> 00:03:57.399
I told you,

00:03:58.160 --> 00:03:59.440
I don't know anything

00:04:05.119 --> 00:04:05.839
Not to mention,

00:04:07.240 --> 00:04:08.759
this Insect-fermented tea from your hometown,

00:04:09.600 --> 00:04:10.880
sounds strange,

00:04:11.119 --> 00:04:12.399
but it tastes really fragrant

00:04:13.160 --> 00:04:13.880
Try some

00:04:14.279 --> 00:04:15.119
see if it's authentic

00:04:37.640 --> 00:04:38.959
These past years haven't been easy, have they?

00:04:40.480 --> 00:04:42.359
Qiao Sanbao was always getting drunk

00:04:42.720 --> 00:04:43.760
and abusing you at home

00:04:44.480 --> 00:04:45.880
To pay for your parents' treatment,

00:04:46.640 --> 00:04:47.760
you've suffered a lot, haven't you?

00:04:49.720 --> 00:04:50.640
As a woman,

00:04:52.119 --> 00:04:52.959
I understand you

00:04:59.760 --> 00:05:00.760
As women,

00:05:01.720 --> 00:05:02.839
we can all understand you

00:05:10.880 --> 00:05:11.799
Understand?

00:05:14.040 --> 00:05:14.920
Beating you,

00:05:15.359 --> 00:05:16.279
You're drunk again

00:05:16.279 --> 00:05:17.399
Don't touch me

00:05:21.480 --> 00:05:22.359
humiliating you,

00:05:23.320 --> 00:05:24.480
I'm your man

00:05:25.119 --> 00:05:26.160
Whenever I want to touch you,

00:05:26.160 --> 00:05:27.239
I'll touch you

00:05:28.359 --> 00:05:30.000
I'm not up for it today

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:31.399
I can't

00:05:32.440 --> 00:05:33.160
Can't?

00:05:34.880 --> 00:05:36.119
Treating you like an object,

00:05:36.119 --> 00:05:37.640
letting others use you like trash,

00:05:39.359 --> 00:05:40.920
how could you understand that?

00:05:41.239 --> 00:05:42.799
Even that Yang guy can touch you,

00:05:42.799 --> 00:05:43.920
so why can't I?

00:05:45.000 --> 00:05:46.600
Convenient or not, make yourself available

00:05:49.320 --> 00:05:50.679
You're the one who owed him money

00:05:50.679 --> 00:05:51.440
and you used me to repay it

00:05:51.440 --> 00:05:53.279
Are you even my man?

00:05:54.880 --> 00:05:55.839
For my parents,

00:05:57.040 --> 00:05:58.119
for this family,

00:05:59.279 --> 00:06:00.079
I could endure it

00:06:03.119 --> 00:06:04.279
A woman's life...

00:06:05.880 --> 00:06:07.359
in this life, it's all fate

00:06:09.880 --> 00:06:10.679
There's no choice

00:06:32.559 --> 00:06:33.359
Please, I beg you

00:06:34.000 --> 00:06:34.799
Please, I beg you

00:06:35.000 --> 00:06:35.399
Please, I beg you

00:06:35.399 --> 00:06:36.160
I was wrong

00:06:36.720 --> 00:06:37.320
I was wrong

00:06:37.720 --> 00:06:38.320
I was wrong

00:06:41.600 --> 00:06:42.839
Did you have no choice

00:06:43.480 --> 00:06:44.640
or were you too scared to fight back

00:06:46.559 --> 00:06:48.600
What has all your endurance gotten you

00:06:52.920 --> 00:06:53.959
What do you mean

00:06:54.720 --> 00:06:55.799
Days like that

00:06:57.000 --> 00:06:58.239
must have been torment every day

00:07:00.559 --> 00:07:02.239
It was like falling into a muddy swamp

00:07:04.000 --> 00:07:05.000
sinking deeper and deeper

00:07:06.040 --> 00:07:07.320
never seeing any light

00:07:09.320 --> 00:07:10.720
Do you feel that

00:07:11.040 --> 00:07:12.359
besides enduring it

00:07:12.720 --> 00:07:13.279
you could not find

00:07:13.279 --> 00:07:14.720
any other way out

00:07:18.959 --> 00:07:20.399
I am the useless one

00:07:20.839 --> 00:07:22.279
Who else can I blame

00:07:23.640 --> 00:07:24.440
You are wrong

00:07:26.600 --> 00:07:28.359
You were just trapped by fear

00:07:28.679 --> 00:07:30.600
Qiao Sanbao controlled you for years

00:07:31.320 --> 00:07:32.799
Even now

00:07:32.799 --> 00:07:34.720
must you still pay for his mistakes

00:07:34.720 --> 00:07:35.839
with your life and your brother's

00:07:35.839 --> 00:07:37.079
and destroy them both

00:07:41.119 --> 00:07:41.920
Liu Li

00:07:44.079 --> 00:07:45.279
Liu Li, look at me

00:07:47.359 --> 00:07:48.720
What you and your brother suffered

00:07:48.920 --> 00:07:50.239
we know very well

00:07:50.880 --> 00:07:52.559
But covering up is not protection

00:07:52.559 --> 00:07:53.679
Neither is silence

00:07:54.880 --> 00:07:56.480
You think you are protecting Liu Ping

00:07:56.480 --> 00:07:57.760
you think you are protecting this family

00:07:58.239 --> 00:08:00.160
But have you ever thought

00:08:00.760 --> 00:08:01.679
that you only gave up

00:08:01.679 --> 00:08:04.000
a chance to reclaim your own life

00:08:04.880 --> 00:08:05.679
I...

00:08:10.119 --> 00:08:11.200
We...

00:08:12.799 --> 00:08:13.600
Then what chance do we

00:08:14.880 --> 00:08:16.920
have left at all

00:08:19.640 --> 00:08:21.359
There are still many chances in life

00:08:21.880 --> 00:08:22.679
Will you choose

00:08:22.679 --> 00:08:23.839
to stay under Qiao Sanbao's

00:08:23.839 --> 00:08:25.160
shadow over you

00:08:25.880 --> 00:08:27.760
and bear the consequences he left you

00:08:28.880 --> 00:08:30.079
or choose to be yourself

00:08:31.399 --> 00:08:32.320
and hold your head up

00:08:33.239 --> 00:08:34.719
for the ones you want to protect

00:08:35.000 --> 00:08:36.280
and make the right choice

00:08:42.599 --> 00:08:43.400
Liu Li

00:08:44.760 --> 00:08:45.640
You are right

00:08:46.640 --> 00:08:48.880
Maybe none of us can truly feel your pain

00:08:49.799 --> 00:08:50.599
But I do know

00:08:51.239 --> 00:08:53.520
the real strength to leave that swamp

00:08:54.159 --> 00:08:55.200
comes from yourself

00:08:55.200 --> 00:08:56.799
the moment you refuse to surrender

00:09:13.159 --> 00:09:14.840
My brother, Liu Ping

00:09:16.520 --> 00:09:18.520
has been sensible since childhood

00:09:19.159 --> 00:09:19.799
Write

00:09:21.080 --> 00:09:23.039
Any dirty or exhausting work

00:09:24.119 --> 00:09:25.119
he could do it all

00:09:28.239 --> 00:09:29.359
But that day

00:09:32.719 --> 00:09:33.760
I also did not know

00:09:34.960 --> 00:09:36.440
what happened to him

00:09:45.960 --> 00:09:46.799
Sanbao

00:09:48.000 --> 00:09:49.159
I will never dare again

00:09:54.000 --> 00:09:54.799
I was wrong

00:09:56.520 --> 00:09:57.320
I was wrong

00:10:04.159 --> 00:10:04.960
Scream

00:10:06.359 --> 00:10:07.440
Scream louder

00:10:07.880 --> 00:10:09.640
Let those people outside playing deaf

00:10:10.200 --> 00:10:11.280
and your useless brother

00:10:12.000 --> 00:10:12.719
hear it

00:10:14.080 --> 00:10:16.039
and see how I discipline a woman

00:10:25.479 --> 00:10:27.000
I am begging you, Sanbao

00:10:30.400 --> 00:10:31.280
He understands everything

00:10:31.400 --> 00:10:32.039
does he not

00:10:32.880 --> 00:10:34.479
What the hell is in that head of yours

00:10:35.919 --> 00:10:37.080
I am begging you

00:10:37.080 --> 00:10:37.880
I was wrong

00:10:38.559 --> 00:10:39.359
Wrong

00:10:45.320 --> 00:10:47.039
If you dare hit my sister again

00:10:48.039 --> 00:10:48.960
I will kill you

00:10:52.880 --> 00:10:53.679
Listen to that

00:10:54.960 --> 00:10:56.559
Your dear brother says he will kill me

00:11:00.200 --> 00:11:00.799
Come on, then

00:11:00.799 --> 00:11:01.280
Kill me

00:11:02.479 --> 00:11:03.280
Do it

00:11:04.960 --> 00:11:06.080
I am telling you

00:11:07.520 --> 00:11:09.320
I am the one feeding your whole family

00:11:10.039 --> 00:11:11.000
Kill me

00:11:11.640 --> 00:11:12.960
and you will all be begging for food

00:11:15.520 --> 00:11:16.400
You came at the right time

00:11:18.960 --> 00:11:20.679
Come see how good I am to your sister

00:11:23.039 --> 00:11:24.239
I just boiled this water

00:11:24.599 --> 00:11:26.320
See how well I treat your sister

00:11:26.640 --> 00:11:27.719
She is dirty

00:11:28.520 --> 00:11:29.559
I am going to wash her up

00:12:12.719 --> 00:12:13.479
Kill one

00:12:13.960 --> 00:12:14.760
it is still killing

00:12:16.359 --> 00:12:17.119
Kill two

00:12:17.840 --> 00:12:18.559
it is still killing

00:12:23.320 --> 00:12:24.119
Sis

00:12:25.239 --> 00:12:27.159
No one will ever bully you again

00:12:27.840 --> 00:12:28.679
Yesterday

00:12:29.479 --> 00:12:31.320
I killed Yang Dazhi too

00:12:59.520 --> 00:13:00.200
Sis

00:13:01.200 --> 00:13:02.840
There is no turning back for me now

00:13:04.960 --> 00:13:05.840
Do not get involved

00:13:08.719 --> 00:13:09.320
I will do it

00:13:37.080 --> 00:13:37.679
Brother San

00:13:38.880 --> 00:13:40.200
The goods from the mountain are good today

00:13:40.200 --> 00:13:41.119
I came to collect again